# BlockApps Letsencrypt Tool

## 1.1.0

- Added the support for STRATO Vault
- Changed the certificate update in STRATO's nginx to be optional

## 1.0.3

- Adjusted the default paths to start with /datadrive

## 1.0.2

- Generate the root user friendly path for suggested strato-getting-started dir when finishing the get-first-cert.sh

## 1.0.1

- Readme enhancements

## 1.0.0

- First release as the stand-alone tool (previously a part of blockapps-rest library)
- More parameters and flexibility to use on hosts with different configurations
- Output the auto-generated crontab command
- Readme changes
